@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Completed
Completed --> Pending : review
Pending --> Archived : update
Pending : entry / log course
Archived --> Reviewed : submit
Reviewed --> Cancelled : process
Cancelled --> Processing : review
Cancelled : entry / log course
Reviewed --> Completed : revert
Processing --> [*]
@enduml